*       APPEND  IT_EMP.
*
*
*
*READ TABLE IT_EMP WITH KEY EMPNO = ENO.
*IF SY-SUBRC = 0.
*        WRITE:/ IT_EMP-EMPNO, IT_EMP-ENAME, IT_EMP-JOB, IT_EMP-SALARY.
*ELSE.
*  MESSAGE I888(SABAPDOCU) WITH 'RECORD DOES NOT EXISTS'.
*  ENDIF.
